text: "Miracles" is a 2010 midwest hip hop song by the American Horrorcore band Insane Clown Posse and is the first single from their eleventh studio album Bang! Pow! Boom!, which was released in 2009. The song was produced by Insane Clown Posse and Mike Clark. The song is also known becoming an internet meme. The music video for the song became viral. It was parodied by Saturday Night Live, which Insane Clown Posse called "a huge honor". ==References== ==Other websites== *Know Your Meme article Category:Insane Clown Posse songs Category:2010 songs Category:Music memes
